content: I think a personalized message would be a great addition to the photo album. I was at a baby shower recently and I made sure to get a gift receipt, just in case my coworker wanted to exchange anything. I purchased her a set of adorable baby clothes and toys from Buy Buy Baby, totaling $100. Anyway, back to the photo album, what's the typical turnaround time for production and shipping? I want to make sure I get it on time for my mom's anniversary.
